{
  "stem": "8786.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They-- and then it was going like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And unfortunately, Hungarian population was ready for it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were looking for the Jewish values, jewelry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well, this was-- this was done before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You were asking me what kind of restrictions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "A Jew was not supposed to have radio, no car, no bicycle, no telephone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was cut off from him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just like-- how shall I say it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To be kept totally, totally cut away from everything which we call normal human life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No schooling.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then came the ghetto time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was already-- most of the husbands, most of the fathers of normal, healthy age, up to about-- up to about 45 or 50, even 55, yes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took in already people who were grandfathers for forced labor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All of a sudden, even I remember those days where pious Jews had to go to the train on the Sabbath or on holiday.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had an uncle in Slovakia who was taken out like this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And just-- he was so over-- he was so shocked from the fact that he has to travel that he fainted just before the train came in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was chopped up to pieces, one of the biggest scholars in the whole-- in the whole country.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was my uncle's brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This happened from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So every healthy middle-aged man, younger middle-aged male, was already not home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now-- now we are up to the point where the ghetto came and we were taken away to a forced labor camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the ghetto, we were taken in by a-- by a Hungarian officer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Horvat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I will have to admit that this man was doing something, a great thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
